    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@vvo \r\n\r\n> Can you give some guidelines as for reviewing every widget, what should we be looking for/paying attention to in those code changes?\r\n\r\nDone in the description.\r\n\r\n> I am using urlSync and upgrade to the latest, will something break?\r\n\r\nno. Worth checking for that.\r\n\r\n> I developed a custom widget and now I will use routing, will something break?\r\n\r\nno. The new methods are optional. You will not benefit from the new routing unless you implement the methods.\r\n\r\n> Do we start deprecating urlSync in favour of routing?\r\n\r\nYes. Also the previous implementation is so badly documented that with a guide, it will be pretty obvious what to choose.\r\n\r\n> If so, let's provide an easy upgrade guide for users of urlSync (link to doc from the code)\r\n\r\nYep. Next PR as for everything doc.",
